{"tid":573749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐怖分子】身世曝光：唉!人地一個咖哩ｎｉｇｇａ　可以做咁多野，真係自慚","createTime":"2018-02-26T17:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T00:30:25.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"23773df395985640f72161042b0b432b88be7c70","tid":573749,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:54:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180227/57879658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57879658&d=8U9gNXKkVFgnT3%2BzTleVlNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=cbac8526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57879658&h=d77e2ee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180227/57879658</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　酸死我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180227/large/1519664955_bb5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180227%2Flarge%2F1519664955_bb5f.jpg&h=99541634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在港落網的「印度重犯」兼恐怖分子Romi，1988年在印度旁遮普邦出生後，移居香港生活，據知曾在玫瑰崗就讀中學。據消息稱，Romi在香港的印度圈相當活躍，早年縱橫重慶大廈，幾乎無人不識，其後他更遭本地黑幫招攬，活躍於東九龍及土瓜灣一帶，他曾自稱為極端恐怖組織伊斯蘭國分支的成員。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》發現Romi在港開設一間公司，登記地址為彩虹邨一個公屋單位。記者晚上到過該單位，惟多次按鐘均無人應門，據附近鄰居所知，單位內住有一家六口，當中包括其父母。根據Romi在Facebook內上載相片可見，有大量2歲愛女的相片，當中不時形容女兒為「Baby Noor」，去年更上載為女兒慶祝生日的相片，恐怖分子瞬間變慈父，此外，他亦育有一名6歲兒子，父子二人更齊齊到芬蘭浴享受一番。據消息稱，Romi的一對子女由前女友所生，早前女友與他鬧翻分手，一對子女就隨父親生活。<br />\n追蹤Romi的fb，發現他雖然移居香港生活，但對家鄉的情況相當關心，又轉載當地的相和片段，更有不少「兄弟」手持獵槍和手槍的照片，每當有家鄉的「兄弟」生日，他都會送上遙遠的祝福。去年3月當地傳媒報道有關轟動印度的劫獄案時，Romi更立即在fb上轉載，看來他非常關心案件。<br />\n至於Romi早前在土瓜灣的「控制室」，《蘋果》記者今午亦到過上址，發現「控制室」設在該單位其中一個劏房，記者按門鐘後，有一名印度女子應門，惟她對記者所有提問均以英語回答「不知道」。有消息稱，其前女友仍居於「控制室」劏房。"},{"pid":"b3e97ac979c9a43498c557f34a412d58b263df83","tid":573749,"uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:56:12.000Z","msg":"公屋仔又升級左連恐怖分子都有埋"},{"pid":"ec0ec0694c3cc4d89c46784b4d463b288ddd1468","tid":573749,"uid":166931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"Nigga係黑人喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebd457da0e6345f22dd0487c49eb1912a021b2f","tid":573749,"uid":59278,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ec0ec0694c3cc4d89c46784b4d463b288ddd1468","tid":573749,"uid":166931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"Nigga係黑人喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔撚識分nigga同呀叉㗎喇<br />\n係又噏唔係又噏好似型啲"},{"pid":"8dbf679f064e359707d279d5bb2a72876b679cda","tid":573749,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bebd457da0e6345f22dd0487c49eb1912a021b2f","tid":573749,"uid":59278,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ec0ec0694c3cc4d89c46784b4d463b288ddd1468","tid":573749,"uid":166931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"Nigga係黑人喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔撚識分nigga同呀叉㗎喇<br />\n係又噏唔係又噏好似型啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"求其喇 <br />\n黑色嫁ma <br />\n咪nigga囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3284843db1803a91d2d15186aeae45008bb7212a","tid":573749